trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A tracking service that implements the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification> interface raises a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event to notify the runtime tracking infrastructure that new instances of a particular workflow <xref:System.Type> should no longer be tracked.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]追蹤服務會實作<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>介面引發<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>事件以通知執行階段追蹤基礎結構的特定工作流程的新執行個體<xref:System.Type>不再進行追蹤。</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service uses a ProfileRemovedEventArgs to provide the workflow <xref:System.Type> to the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: 追蹤服務會提供工作流程使用 ProfileRemovedEventArgs<xref:System.Type>至執行階段追蹤基礎結構。</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> uses a ProfileRemovedEventArgs when it raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=fullName> event.

After a tracking service raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event, the runtime tracking infrastructure will no longer associate a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> with the specified workflow <xref:System.Type> for that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: 追蹤服務之後引發<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>事件，執行階段追蹤基礎結構就不再會將<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>與指定的工作流程<xref:System.Type>該追蹤服務。</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: If you use this constructor when you raise a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event inside a tracking service, you must explicitly set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 如果您使用這個建構函式，當您將提高<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>事件追蹤服務，您必須明確設定<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"></xref> class that applies to the specified workflow <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"></xref>套用至指定的工作流程<xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type>的類別

trans-unit.source: A new instance of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> is created with <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> set to the specified <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs>建立與<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>設定為指定<xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A></xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs>的新執行個體

trans-unit.source: The workflow <xref:System.Type> for which the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> should be removed.
trans-unit.target: 工作流程<xref:System.Type>其<xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref>應加以移除。</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the workflow <xref:System.Type> for which the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> should be removed.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定工作流程<xref:System.Type>其<xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref>應加以移除。</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: WorkflowType specifies the workflow <xref:System.Type> for which a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> no longer exists, and which, therefore, should no longer be tracked by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: WorkflowType 指定工作流程<xref:System.Type>其<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>不再存在，及，因此，應該不會再追蹤執行階段追蹤基礎結構。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Type>
